projects.name: About Sam
projects.subtitle: Jack of all Trades
projects.abstract: As a Jack-of-all trades I am always keeping busy. I am a skateboarder for more than ten years and am currently ride for a local skateshop, Loco Skate Shop in Longmont Colorado. Also an advid lover of adventuring and exploring new places, be it here in Colorado or further. Though I always find time to create new things, be it rugs or artwork, 3D models, or programs and games

projects.name: Cyberfrog
projects.subtitle: The Colorado Nasa Space Grant Project
projects.abstract: This is the FRCC Cyberfrog! At Front Range Community College I had the oppertunity and privalege to lead the robotics team. Going on to lead the team to participate in the NASA Colorado Space Grand Consortium, where we were tasked with creating an autonomous mars rover the size of a house cat.
